data.description: BEST VALUE IN SOUGHT AFTER COMMUNITY OF HAGERS CROSSING, BASED ON SQUARE FOOTAGE OF THE HOUSE/BASEMENT/GARAGE, QUALITY CONSTRUCTION, & LOT SIZE!!   *Great HOA Community amenities include: pools, gym, basketball court, tennis court, playgrounds, picnic tables, and a beautiful club house for private and community parties.   *Access to 270 for work/life balance for commuters to  Washington D.C., Montgomery County and Northern Virginia.  Hagerstown is beautiful and it has a lot to offer for dining, sight seeing, sports, shopping, antiquing, and entertainment! *This is a 3.5 bath, 4 bedroom, 3341 Square foot house, with a gourmet kitchen, granite island & counter tops, a beautiful sun room, a private office with French doors, a marble front, gas, fire place with crown molding, and a grand mantel in the living room.   There is also a separate, formal dining room. *The walkout basement has a full bath and it's a finished basement, which hosts a massive game room,  a theater room, utilities room, and plenty of storage.    *This beautiful house is in good condition and will pass inspections.  It simply needs some new carpet, kitchen flooring, and a fresh coat of interior paint, before you move in.  All cosmetic work should be to your own taste.  The owner will give the buyer a concession at closing, with a full price offer.
